 from bassili cs arizona edu amgad z bassili subject copt net newsletter four lines one eight this is to let you know that the fourth issue of the copt net newsletter has been issued the highlights of this issue include one easter greating christ is risen truly he is risen two the holy family in egypt part one three anba abraam the friend of the poor part four four a review of the coptic encyclopedia five a new dictionary of the coptic language this newsletter has been prepared by members of copt net a forum where news activities and services of the coptic orthodox churches and coptic communities outside egypt are coordinated and exchanged if you want your name to be included in the mailing list or have any questions please contact nabil ayoub at copt net editorial board